#: ../../src/developer/troubleshooting.rst:8
msgid "If you experience errors only on a dedicated environment such as ``prod``, ``dev`` or ``install``, it means that cache is not fresh for these environments. As a first try, you should always call ``bin/roadiz cache:clear -e prod;`` (replace *prod* by your environment) in command line."
msgstr ""

