#: ../../src/developer/troubleshooting.rst:41
msgid "If you are behind a reverse-proxy like *Varnish* or *Nginx proxy* on a *Docker* environment, IP addresses, domain name and proto (https/http) could not be correctly set. So you will have to `tell Roadiz to trust your proxy <https://symfony.com/doc/3.4/deployment/proxies.html#solution-settrustedproxies>`_ in order to use ``X_FORWARDED_*`` env vars."
